{"tid":1633060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【反思】撫心自問有冇盡力保護自己同前線","createTime":"2019-10-07T02:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T03:43:17.000Z","uid":218211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a68b9fb767f9e2efea8ab91c7bc3c261b54b39fe","tid":1633060,"uid":218211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"話說琴日發夢見到好多人<br />\n都仲係著條短褲就出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都算啦<br />\n都仲淨係戴住個口罩<br />\n頭又唔包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家知唔知咩係<strong>Black Bloc</strong>？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑衫、黑長褲、黑鞋、黑帽、黑口罩/ 黑頭巾</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亦都強烈建議用黑T-shirt做頭巾，包晒成個頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FSsGEeQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFSsGEeQ.jpg&h=03c9f71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好處</span><br />\n<br />\n1. <strong>保護自己</strong>，啲狗點影都得對眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. <strong>保護前線</strong>，控方搜證極有難度（要拍攝整個過程）<br />\n<br />\n3. 如用T-shirt包頭，解左又可以換，佢又話唔到你蒙面，又通風過口罩<br />\n<br />\nBossini都係賣緊三十幾蚊件渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你睇下，鬼知你邊個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykGcL1N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykGcL1N.jpg&h=f4abd006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc  BlackBloc</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我係到真心求下大家準備好先好出黎</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港  時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"9938837b970a092ea038d1fe100c2e659ea52c34","tid":1633060,"uid":218211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:12:12.000Z","msg":"Black Bloc 1/100"},{"pid":"613c227879815d5909b3a2ceb3d23dbdf23a6e32","tid":1633060,"uid":218211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:12:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\